<span class="label">ACM TechNews</span>
<h2>Tesla Recalls 2 Million Cars with 'Insufficient' Autopilot Safety Controls</h2>
<h6 class="subheader"></h6>
</div>
<hr class="dotted" />
<div id="articleFullText" class="col1 floatLeft firstCol">
<span class="byline">
By The Washington Post
<br/>
December 18, 2023<br/>
<a href="#comments">Comments</a>
</span>
